Caption: humanrace Samba Colors by pharrell     The elevated iteration of our Iconic Samba silhouette is a celebration of craftsmanship high-quality materials and colorways that embody the diversity of Humanrace’s DNA.   Made with all-around premium leather upper leather lining and leather shoelaces from ECCO Leather. The raw materials are transformed into the adidas Samba Leather through eccoleather’s water-saving tanning technology which saves 20 liters of water per hide resulting in higher color fastness and better performance. The extended tongue is a nod to the Samba’s rich football heritage.  Now available on humanrace.com and CONFIRMED – hit the link in bio to shop. #adidasPharrellWilliams
